#define START_HOUSENUMBER_DIR_MASK   0x00038000
 

Start housenumber direction code mask.

3 bit. The eight values are: 0 - unknown_oddeven_t 1 - leftOddRightEven 2 - rightOddLeftEven 3 - unknown_nbr_t 4 - increasing 5 - decreasing 6 - reserved 7 - reserved
